24union _FP_UNION_Q
25{
26 __float128 flt;
27 struct
28 {
29 unsigned long frac0 : 32;
30 unsigned long frac1 : 32;
31 unsigned long frac2 : 32;
32 unsigned long frac3 : 16;
33 unsigned exp : 15;
34 unsigned sign : 1;
35 } bits __attribute__((packed));
36};
37
38__float128 __copysigntf3 (__float128, __float128);
39__float128 __fabstf2 (__float128);
40
41__float128
42__copysigntf3 (__float128 a, __float128 b)
43{
44 union _FP_UNION_Q A, B;
45
46 A.flt = a;
47 B.flt = b;
48 A.bits.sign = B.bits.sign;
49
50 return A.flt;
51}
52
53__float128
54__fabstf2 (__float128 a)
55{
56 union _FP_UNION_Q A;
57
58 A.flt = a;
59 A.bits.sign = 0;
60
61 return A.flt;
62}
